Featuring Snoop Dogg, WC, and Ice-T

	Straight off the streets of South Central Los Angeles, CJ Mac, along with multi-platinum-selling artist Snoop Dogg, WC, Ice-T, Kurupt, Warren G, Ras Kass, Malik Yoba, and Jonathan Davis, brings you C-WALK, a documentary about a gang ritual that has become a popular dance craze.  Not only will you hear the opinions from the artist that made the C-Walk mainstream through videos and live performances, you will also hear from the Original Crip Gang members who started the walk.  Is it a dance or a gang ritual?  You decide.
